    <title>Mac下创建属于自己的博客（github pages with hexo）</title>
    <link href="http://www.xuzc.me/2016/12/22/mac-github-pages-with-domain/"/>
    <id>http://www.xuzc.me/2016/12/22/mac-github-pages-with-domain/</id>
    <published>2016-12-22T02:49:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-12-22T09:25:59.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><ul>
<li><p>mac 版本号： <figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>```</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">* git 版本号： ``` git version 2.7.4 (Apple Git-66)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</li>
<li><p>node 版本号：<figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>```</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">* npm 版本号：``` 3.10.9</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</li>
<li><p>github 帐号</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>注：其中node安装包中已集成了npm，所以安装node即代表已安装了npm （<a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v6.9.2/node-v6.9.2.pkg" target="_blank" rel="external">node最新稳定版下载地址</a>）</p>
<h2 id="开始"><a href="#开始" class="headerlink" title="开始"></a>开始</h2><h3 id="安装-hexo-官方中文文档"><a href="#安装-hexo-官方中文文档" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo 官方中文文档"></a>安装 hexo <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="external">官方中文文档</a></h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo --save</div><div class="line">$ npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>验证是否安装成功</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo -v</div><div class="line">$ npm -v</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="使用-hexo-创建项目"><a href="#使用-hexo-创建项目" class="headerlink" title="使用 hexo 创建项目"></a>使用 hexo 创建项目</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo init blog //其中blog是本地的工作目录，按照个人喜好命名</div><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</div><div class="line">$ npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>如果在blog目录下看到这样的目录结构就说明创建成功：<br><img src="/images/Mac-github-pages-with-hexo/mac-github-pages-with-hexo-01.png" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="与-github-项目绑定"><a href="#与-github-项目绑定" class="headerlink" title="与 github 项目绑定"></a>与 github 项目绑定</h3><p>注意：必须创建一个以自己的github帐号名称为前缀形如 <figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>```的github项目</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"></div><div class="line">``` bash</div><div class="line">$ vim _config.yml</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>修改：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repository: https://github.com/&lt;account-name&gt;/&lt;account-name&gt;.github.io.git</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>注：其中<figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>```指的是github帐号名称，例如我的是 ``` xuzc ```</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"></div><div class="line">### 生成博客页面并发布</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">``` bash</div><div class="line">$ hexo g -d  // g是generate的简写, d是deploy的简写，文件生成后立即部署网站</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>如果想清除缓存，重新生成所有页面：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo clean</div><div class="line">$ hexo g <span class="_">-d</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="与个人域名绑定（Godaddy）"><a href="#与个人域名绑定（Godaddy）" class="headerlink" title="与个人域名绑定（Godaddy）"></a>与个人域名绑定（Godaddy）</h3><p>在DNS管理面板上，添加：<br><img src="/images/Mac-github-pages-with-hexo/mac-github-pages-with-hexo-02.png" alt=""></p>
]]></content>
    
